+ * Usage:
+ *   node scripts/csi-spectrogram.js --file data/recordings/pretrain-1775182186.csi.jsonl --ascii
+ *   node scripts/csi-spectrogram.js --live --port 5006 --ingest --seed-url https://169.254.42.1:8443
